"title": "Isaka",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "isaka",
"language": "swh",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jina Isaka linamaanisha &quot;anacheka,&quot; ambalo linaonyesha jinsi alivyokuwa amezaliwa. Wakati Mungu aliahidi kuzaliwa kwa Isaka, wote Abrahamu na Sara walicheka kwa kutoamini (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:15-Gen17:19\">Mwanzo 17:15–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:9-Gen18:15\">18:9–15</a>). Mungu alikuwa ameahidi Abrahamu mwana (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:4-Gen15:6\">Mwanzo 15:4–6</a>). Hata hivyo, hakuna mwana aliyekuja, na Abrahamu na Sara walikuwa wazee sana kupata watoto. Kwa hiyo, wakati Isaka alizaliwa, walicheka kwa furaha (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:6-Gen21:7\">Mwanzo 21:6–7</a>).</p><p>Wakati Isaka alipokuwa kijana, Mungu alimjaribu Abrahamu kwa kumwambia amtoe Isaka kuwa dhabihu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:1-Gen22:19\">Mwanzo 22:1–19</a>). Imani ya Abrahamu ilibaki thabiti. Alitii na Isaka alijisalimisha kwake. Mungu kisha aliingilia kati na kutoa kondoo dume kwa dhabihu badala ya Isaka. Kwa sababu ya imani ya Abrahamu, Mungu aliahidi baraka kubwa (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:15-Gen22:18\">Mwanzo 22:15–18</a>).</p><p>Isaka alimuoa Rebeka na alikuwa tayari kuendeleza ukoo ulioteuliwa, lakini Rebeka hakuweza kupata watoto (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:21\">Mwanzo 25:21</a>). Badala ya kujaribu kutatua matatizo mwenyewe kama Baba yake alivyofanya (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:1-Gen16:16\">Mwanzo 16:1–16</a>), Isaka alimwomba Bwana, na Rebeka alizaa watoto mapacha wa kiume. Isaka alimpenda Esau, mwana mkubwa, wakati Rebeka alimpenda Yakobo. Upendeleo huu ulisababisha Yakobo kumdanganya Isaka alipokuwa mzee na kipofu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:1-Gen27:40\">Mwanzo 27:1–40</a>). Upendeleo uliendelea kuwa tatizo miongoni mwa wazao wa Isaka (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:30\">Mwanzo 29:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:1-Gen33:2\">33:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:4\">37:4</a>).</p><p>Isaka alifuata mfano wa baba yake Abrahamu katika kushughulika na mataifa jirani. Wakati wa njaa, alitembelea ufalme mwingine na, kwa hofu, akasema kwamba mke wake ni dada yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1-Gen26:11\">Mwanzo 26:1–11</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10-Gen12:20\">12:10–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:1-Gen20:18\">20:1–18</a>). Kama baba yake, Isaka alifanikiwa katika nchi hiyo na aliombwa kuondoka (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:12-Gen26:16\">Mwanzo 26:12–16</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:16-Gen12:20\">12:16–20</a>). Alikabiliana na migogoro juu ya maji na ardhi na wachungaji wengine (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:17-Gen26:22\">Mwanzo 26:17–22</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:25-Gen21:31\">21:25–31</a>). Pia alifanya agano na mfalme wa Wafilisti (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:26-Gen26:31\">Mwanzo 26:26–31</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:22-Gen21:32\">21:22–32</a>).</p><p>Isaka alipokea ahadi sawa na baba yake (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:2-Gen26:5\">Mwanzo 26:2–5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:23-Gen26:25\">23–25</a>; linganisha <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:16-Gen22:18\">22:16–18</a>). Alionyesha kujitolea kwake kwa kuendeleza desturi ya tohara, ambayo iliwakilisha agano (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:8\">Matendo 7:8</a>). Kama mtoto wa ahadi, Isaka anawakilisha wote ambao ni watoto wa Abrahamu kupitia imani katika Kristo. Wao ni huru kuishi kama watoto wa Mungu, si kama watumwa (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:21-Gal5:1\">Wagalatia 4:21–5:1</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:19-Gen17:21\">Mwanzo 17:19–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:1-Gen21:12\">21:1–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:1-Gen22:19\">22:1–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:1-Gen24:8\">24:1–8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:14\">14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:62-Gen24:67\">62–67</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:5-Gen25:11\">25:5–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:19-Gen25:28\">19–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:1-Gen28:9\">26:1–28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:42\">31:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:12\">35:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:27-Gen35:28\">27–28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:15-Gen48:16\">48:15–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:31\">49:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:6\">Kutoka 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:3-Josh24:4\">Yoshua 24:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:6-Rom9:10\">Warumi 9:6–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:21-Gal4:31\">Wagalatia 4:21–31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:8-Heb11:9\">Waebrania 11:8–9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:17-Heb11:20\">17–20</a></p>",
